description: We focus on premium design and ideal form, fit and function for the ultimate tablet experience. The high quality materials, precision design and fine styling of our Google Nexus 7 case ensure reliable performance and high satisfaction. Should any concern arise, OtterBox handles every situation with hassle-free, industry-defining customer service. Enjoy your work everywhere with confidence that your Google Nexus 7 is protected and functions flawlessly while inside a highly protective and rugged Defender Series case. Get the kind of protection that inspires confidence with the Defender Series Google Nexus 7 case from OtterBox.
title: OtterBox Defender Series Hybrid Case with Screen Protector and Stand for the Nexus 7 (First Generation) - Black
